Relief Work Data Analytics Platform

Non-profits can use our Analytics platform powered by AWS Athena to analyze demographics data to find right areas which need help and also what kind of help is needed.

Once a target area and field of choice is decided, we help non profits find the right partners as well as volunteers using our analytics platform.

Get Started!
Step 1: Select a category of analytical data you want.
Step 2: Drill down to analyze the data at state level
Step 3: Select a County to analyse further

Welcome to SevaBhava

We see a lot of amazing people taking up initiatives to help unorganized workers, migrant workers, families living in slums, stray animals through various means and resources. These people often run short of support as not everyone can generate awareness about all the social work they are doing.

This led to a thought on why not create a platform where people can find all the social work happening in their area on a map and connect with them. SevaBhava is a platform just made for that.

Search Pune and click on the help to see how it works.
